Creator: Christian Tatem Lee
Contact: ChristianTatemLee@Gmail.com

Android application built with a responsive layout and plenty of personality.
Built with Java, XML, SQLite, and Room.

About Tall Tale: a reading tracker to help user's "read as tall as they are."
Enter the books you're reading, Physical, Digital, or Audio books, and the app
will make a virtual stack of them until that pil of books is as tall as you are!

How to use: The app has a handy little introductory graphic that you can access on the login screen. Just hit the "i" icon.

Feel free to download the app and try it out.

